&lt;p&gt;该回答引用ChatGPT&lt;br /&gt;首先&amp;#xff0c;创建一个新的MATLAB GUI应用程序。在APP Designer中&amp;#xff0c;您可以选择&amp;#34;Blank App&amp;#34;&amp;#xff0c;然后选择&amp;#34;Create&amp;#34;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在UI界面上&amp;#xff0c;添加一个&amp;#34;Edit Field&amp;#34;组件和一个&amp;#34;Push Button&amp;#34;组件。将&amp;#34;Edit Field&amp;#34;组件的&amp;#34;Tag&amp;#34;属性设置为&amp;#34;inputField&amp;#34;&amp;#xff0c;&amp;#34;Push Button&amp;#34;组件的&amp;#34;Tag&amp;#34;属性设置为&amp;#34;plotButton&amp;#34;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在APP Designer中&amp;#xff0c;单击&amp;#34;Code View&amp;#34;按钮&amp;#xff0c;将以下代码添加到相应的回调函数中&amp;#xff1a;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash"&gt;&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% --- Executes on button press in plotButton.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="hljs-function"&gt;&lt;span class="hljs-keyword"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hljs-title"&gt;plotButtonPushed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hljs-params"&gt;(app, event)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% 获取输入的参数&lt;/span&gt;
inputVal &amp;#61; app.inputField.Value;

&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% 将字符串转换为数字&lt;/span&gt;
x &amp;#61; str2double(inputVal);

&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% 检查输入值是否在范围内&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="hljs-keyword"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hljs-built_in"&gt;isnan&lt;/span&gt;(x) || x &amp;lt;&amp;#61; &lt;span class="hljs-number"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; || x &amp;gt; &lt;span class="hljs-number"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
errordlg(&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;Invalid input. Please enter a number between 1 and 10.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;Error&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;modal&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;span class="hljs-keyword"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% 根据输入值生成随机数据&lt;/span&gt;
y &amp;#61; &lt;span class="hljs-built_in"&gt;rand&lt;/span&gt;(x,&lt;span class="hljs-number"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;);


&lt;span class="hljs-comment"&gt;% 绘制随机数据的图形&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="hljs-built_in"&gt;plot&lt;/span&gt;(app.UIAxes, y);
title(app.UIAxes, sprintf(&lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;Random Data with %d Points&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, x));
xlabel(app.UIAxes, &lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;Index&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
ylabel(app.UIAxes, &lt;span class="hljs-string"&gt;&amp;#39;Value&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
